<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-12-19T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-12-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="546" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d546">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/758.]</note>
                        <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-12-19">
                                    <hi rend="italic">December 19, 1912</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Horacio Vásquez yesterday issued an open letter to the country announcing
                            his retirement from politics for the present, and declaring his perfect
                            confidence in the Archbishop, with whose administration Vásquez promises
                            not to interfere.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>